    {
      "id": "line-000",
      "start": 0.58,
      "end": 5.42,
      "text": "This is a LibraVox recording. All LibraVox recordings are in the public domain.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-001",
      "start": 6.28,
      "end": 10.46,
      "text": "For more information or to volunteer, please visit LibraVox.org.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-002",
      "start": 11.68,
      "end": 14.8,
      "text": "ASOP's Fables, the Kid on the House top.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 15.58,
      "end": 21.26,
      "text": "A kid climbed up on the roof of an outhouse, attracted by the grass and other things that grew in the thatch.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 21.92,
      "end": 28.92,
      "text": "And as he stood there browsing away, he caught sight of a wolf passing below and jeered at him because he couldn't reach him.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 28.92,
      "end": 37.42,
      "text": "The wolf only looked up and said, I hear you, my young friend, but it is not you who mock me, but the roof on which you are standing.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 38.46,
      "end": 41.54,
      "text": "End of the Kid on the House top.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
